OL,3,CWhat is a 'flabby high' and what is
OL,4,Cthe truth behind the 'Arctic plunge'?
OL,6,FTwo weeks of warm and sunny weather
OL,7,Fhas given way to something rather more
OL,8,Fseasonal this week - cooler
OL,9,Ftemperatures, cloudier skies and
OL,10,Fovernight frosts.
OL,12,FHere's everything you need to know
OL,13,Fabout the weather over the next few
OL,14,Fdays.
OL,16,FIs it really getting much colder?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat is a 'flabby high' and what is
OL,4,Cthe truth behind the 'Arctic plunge'?
OL,6,FYes! And no. When you compare our
OL,7,Fmidweek high temperatures of just 7C
OL,8,For 8C in the north and 15C in the
OL,9,Fsouth to the peak of the heat last
OL,10,Fweek, that represents around a ten
OL,11,Fdegree drop in temperature - which is
OL,12,Fboth noticeable and dramatic in such a
OL,13,Fshort space of time.
OL,15,FOn the other hand, it was last week's
OL,16,Fheat that was exceptional rather than
OL,17,Fthe cooler values this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
