FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat is a 'flabby high' and what is
OL,4,Cthe truth behind the 'Arctic plunge'?
OL,6,FMaybe! And it's definitely needed
OL,7,Facross large swathes of the UK. There
OL,8,Fis the potential for a band of heavy
OL,9,Frain to move in across the south of
OL,10,Fthe UK through the early part of the
OL,11,Fweekend, which would be welcome news
OL,12,Ffor farmers who are starting to become
OL,13,Fvery anxious about the lack of rain so
OL,14,Ffar this spring.
OL,16,FHowever, there is also every chance
OL,17,Fthat that area of rain may take a
OL,18,Fdifferent track and stay offshore and
OL,19,Faway from us - so stay up to date with
OL,20,Fthe latest on this situation if you're
OL,21,Falso anxiously watching and waiting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
